## 3) Boucles: `for`, `while`, `do...while`

```javascript
// for
for (let i = 1; i <= 10; i++) {
  console.log(i);
}

// while
let i = 1;
while (i <= 3) {
  console.log("while:", i);
  i++;
}

// do...while (s’exécute au moins une fois)
let j = 0;
do {
  console.log("do...while:", j);
  j++;
} while (j < 2);
```

